column5: needs help!!   irecently read an article ina magazine about a new lure that is out for walleye,,,It's see through except for  some shiney material imbedded in it,,,can anyone here remember the name of the lure,,,,wishing to find out who has it locally,,,but not much help if ya don't know the name,,lol thanks
could it be the glass shad rap?
